# Advisory output directory for the `spec-monitor` Claude Skill (`novel/spec-monitor/`).
#
# Files written here are named `<YYYY-MM-DD>.md` and contain advisory
# tables (rule_id / evidence / severity / suggested_repair). They are
# never load-bearing for CI — per rule #10, advisory output cannot gate
# a merge. The Skill writes; reviewers read.
#
# Empty file kept so the directory is tracked.
